<法規>
<法規性質>命令</法規性質>
<英文法規名稱>Regulations on the Reporting of Fishing Operations of Foreign Flag Fishing Vessels Invested by a Taiwan National</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>投資經營非我國籍漁船作業資料申報辦法</中文法規名稱>
<法規網址>http://law.moj.gov.tw/Eng/LawClass/LawContent.aspx?PCODE=M0050040</法規網址>
<最新英文異動日期>20091016</最新英文異動日期>
<廢止註記>
</廢止註記>
<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Promulgated on October 16, 2009]]></沿革內容>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Regulations (hereinafter referred to as "the Regulations") are　established pursuant to Article 5 paragraph 2 of the Ordinance to Govern Investment in the Operation of Foreign Flag Fishing Vessels.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Any Taiwan national who has been authorized to invest and operate a foreign flag fishing vessel fishing in sea areas beyond national jurisdiction, shall report in electronic or written form between 1 and 28 February every year its fishing operations of the preceding year to the competent authority.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Report of fishing operations referred to in the preceding article shall include the following information:
1. Fishing period;
2. Fishery type;
3. Targeted species;
4. Weight of catch;
5. Time for the sale of catch, quantity of catch sold and buying countries.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The regulations shall be effective upon promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
